But it wasn't just bullets that proved ineffective against Albino's might. As he rounded a corner, he sensed a man hiding behind a thick concrete wall, his gun held tightly, waiting for the opportunity to use the tiny screen-door to land a shot on Albino's advancing form. With a casual flick of his wrist, Albino's hands shot forward, easily punching through the solid barrier as if it were made of paper. The man's eyes widened in horror as Albino seized him by the throat and dragged him out forcefully into the open, tearing a hole into the wall in the process, his fate sealed in an instant as Albino crushed his head with a sickening crunch.
